  <Name>Aganazzar's Scorcher</Name>
  <CastingTime>1 action</CastingTime>
  <Range>30 feet</Range>
  <Duration>Instantaneous</Duration>
  <Level>2</Level>
  <Description>A line of roaring flame 30 feet long and 5 feet wide emanates from you in a direction you choose. Each creature in the line must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 3d8 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</Description>
  <Descriptions>
    <Description>
      <Name>At Higher Levels</Name>
      <Text>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 2nd.</Text>
    </Description>
  </Descriptions>
